### **4. 33_LiveChartTunnel**  
**Description:**  
Scrolls numeric live data into a real-time chart with a tunnel-like animated view.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveChartTunnel - Realtime Data Stream Visualizer

LiveChartTunnel displays incoming data in a smooth scrolling timeline, perfect for metrics, experiments, or dashboards.

## Features
- Live scrollable plot  
- Adjustable update interval  
- Matplotlib backend  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_LiveChartTunnel.git
cd 33_LiveChartTunnel
python visualize.py
